Allows the user to modify, add or delete recording schedule entries.
Client has to be @dfn{super} to make modifications here.
For @dfn{RST_DAY} type recordings to update properly,
individual weekdays have to be selected. 
Users in countries with Daylight Savings Time have to modify their 
recording schedules on each transition as the program uses GMT 
internally and is not DST aware. @key{s} shows all currently running recordings. 
